    "title": "Vacancy for Financial Analyst at HDFC Life Insurance",
    "description": "Grow your career with HDFC Life Insurance! We are hiring a Financial Analyst for our Mumbai team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout HDFC Life Insurance:\nHDFC Life Insurance is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with HDFC Life Insurance!",
